eZp Enhanced Link Check script README

What is the eZp Enhanced Link Check extension?
================================

eZp Enhanced Link Check is a true eZ Publish extension
that provides a customized commandline script to test
for valid links in content


eZp Enhanced Link Check version
=======================

The current version of eZp Enhanced Link Check is 0.1.0
Last Major update: October 21, 2013


