Requirements
============

The following requirements exists for using eZp Enhanced Link Check extension:

o  eZ Publish version:

   Make sure you use eZ Publish version 4.x (required) or higher. eZ Publish 4.6.x+ (Community Build, 2011.11+) is recommended.

o  PHP version:

   Make sure you have PHP 5.x or higher.


Usage - Command line script
============

# Change directory into eZ Publish website document root:
cd path/to/ezpublish/docroot;

# Run the script to generate the report
php ./extension/ezpenhancedlinkcheck/bin/shell/runcronjobpart-ezpenhancedlinkcheck.sh


Usage - Cronjob
============

# Change directory into eZ Publish website document root:
cd path/to/ezpublish/docroot;

# Run the cronjob manually to check links
php ./runcronjobs.php ezpenhancedlinkcheck


Usage - Module
============

# Click the new "Link Check" menu tab and follow the instructions on the page.

http://admin.example.com/enhancedlinkcheck/urls


